> > Take a pair of channel lock pliers and brace them against the 
> engine
> > block and pull your tubes out.
> 
> to clearify that a little, the push rods come out through the
> heads. unlike the older engines in which they were squeezed between 
> the
> head and block.
> 
> so        |           |
>     block |___________|  head
>                cyl      
>            ___________
>           |           |
>            ===========   <-pushrod tube
>           |           |
> 
>       it comes out---> this way--->
